flowRoot.flowPara: recipe to get the coordinate of the center of the router_bit in the smooth corner:
1.1- compute R1 the radius of the first arc
1.2- get the orientation of the first arc (CCW or CW)
1.3- get the angle of the intersection in the first arc
1.4- with 1.2 and 1.3 get the angle of the tangent (speed direction) at the intersection in the first arc
2.1- compute R2 the radius of the second arc
2.2- get the orientation of the second arc (CCW or CW)
2.3- get the angle of the intersection in the second arc
2.4- with 2.2 and 2.3 get the angle of the tangent (speed direction) at the intersection in the second arc
3.1- compute the angle between the two tangents at the intersection and check its sign
S and the intersection are on the same side compare to (IJ)
